{"tid":2208361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"再次封城？英國確診個案反彈，約翰遜不排除再推全國限制措施","createTime":"2020-09-19T00:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T12:53:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2ba5ae0319752df71ae49602560b81e3a6591b72","tid":2208361,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:10:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550468-20200919.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550468-20200919.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=4b35363e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550468-20200919.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2bc7a427\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550468-20200919.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜表示，正看到第二波新型肺炎的疫情出現，不排除要在全國推出新的限制措施。約翰遜表明不希望實施第二輪全國封鎖，但政府必須考慮是否需要推出進一步措施。<br />\n<br />\n英國近期的確診個案，每日平均達到6千宗，確診個案較之前差不多增加一倍，英格蘭北部和倫敦部分地區的入院人數增加，感染率飆升。英國目前有超過38萬8千人確診，4萬1千人死亡，死亡人數是全球第5多。"},{"pid":"c1593b1cc257a4b536f50421ba264f339d97df2d","tid":2208361,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520c7b1dc234bea1ce75527b25d9ffb2b540ecc7","tid":2208361,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:25:50.000Z","msg":"Eat out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35d9f1c639ca9ff3400cff6399c99ae8d0d431e","tid":2208361,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"520c7b1dc234bea1ce75527b25d9ffb2b540ecc7","tid":2208361,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T00:25:50.000Z","msg":"Eat out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi